    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it's time for my pride and joy to find a new garage. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, strictly hand-washed, and kept in absolutely stunning condition. It still has that 'new car' feel and the paint has a deep, mirror-like shine that photos just don't do justice. There\u2019s a tiny, almost invisible stone chip on the lower bumper if you really go looking for it, but otherwise, she\u2019s a total dream and drives smooth as silk. If you're looking for a pristine ride that\u2019s been truly loved, you\u2019ve found it!",
      "price": 48500.0,
