      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level example of automotive engineering, meticulously maintained for the discerning pilot. This chassis features a laser-aligned suspension geometry with uprated bushings for zero deflection under high-G loads. The powerplant has been optimized with a high-flow induction system and a bespoke ECU map that sharpens throttle response across the entire power band. We've performed a comprehensive top-end refresh, ensuring the valvetrain operates with surgical precision. The paintwork boasts a multi-stage ceramic infusion, preserving that factory-fresh depth. This isn't just a car; it's a turn-key performance machine with a rock-solid drivetrain and a cockpit that remains hermetically sealed from the elements. No expense spared on preventative maintenance\u2014this unit is ready for the track or the collection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
