      "description": "This isn't just a vehicle; it's a captured moment of automotive perfection. Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through winding coastal roads, the engine humming a low, rhythmic lullaby that speaks of heritage and power. Every curve of its shimmering silhouette has been polished to a mirror-like sheen, reflecting a world of pure elegance. Inside, the scent of rich, preserved leather welcomes you into a cabin that feels untouched by time, a sanctuary where every dial and stitch tells a story of unparalleled craftsmanship. To drive this masterpiece is to command the very essence of the open road.",
      "price": 48500.0,
