      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Thanks for taking a look at my pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and it shows\u2014she\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition and drives like a dream. I\u2019ve always kept her tucked away in the garage and treated her with the utmost care. It\u2019s rare to find one kept this clean, and while it\u2019s tough to say goodbye, I\u2019m excited for her to go to someone who will appreciate those smooth lines as much as I do. She\u2019s practically perfect and ready for your next Sunday cruise!",
