    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a surgical-grade example of automotive engineering, maintained to tolerances that exceed factory specifications. The heart of this machine features a blueprinted top-end with port-matched induction for optimized volumetric efficiency and a recalibrated ECU map that ensures a perfectly linear torque curve. The drivetrain has been enhanced with a lightweight, high-inertia flywheel and a zero-lash short-throw shifter for crisp, mechanical engagement. To sharpen the handling, I\u2019ve refined the suspension geometry with adjustable control arms and corner-balanced coilovers, significantly reducing unsprung weight and eliminating body roll. Every bushing has been inspected for structural integrity, and the thermal management system has been upgraded with a high-flow aluminum radiator. This isn't just a car; it's a meticulously indexed performance tool with a mirror-finish aesthetic that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment. No parasitic draws, no fluid weeping\u2014just pure, high-output mechanical synergy.",
